<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT1.7">
<l>cuḻalu maḻalviḻik koḷḷi vāyppēy cūḻntu tuṇaṅkaiyiṭ ṭōṭi yāṭit</l>
<l>taḻalu ḷeriyum piṇattai vāṅkit tāṉṟaṭi tiṉṟaṇaṅ kāṭu kāṭṭiṟ</l>
<l>kaḻaloli yōcaic cilampo lippak kāluyar vaṭṭaṇai yiṭṭu naṭṭa</l>
<l>maḻalumiḻn tōri katikka vāṭu mappa ṉiṭamtiru vālaṅ kāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of our father who dances, so that [his] mane moves rapidly, spitting fire,</l>
<l>[his] dance, setting up a circular course, feet high so that [his] loosening noisy anklets sound,</l> 
<l>in the cremation ground where demonesses, with eyes that are whirling fires, with firebrand mouths, circle,</l>
<l>putting up a Tuṇaṅkai, running [and] dancing, dragging corpses that are ignited in the fire, eating the flesh, dance terribly,</l>
<l>is Tiruvalaṅkāṭu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
